INTRODUCTION: Use vxperf2 to analyze, summarize and visualize any text databases. (e.g. Logs generated by any OS monitoring tool.)
REQUIRED: Perl, Gnuplot
INSTALLATION: perl install.pl
DOCUMENTATION: perldoc vxperf2, perldoc log2db
BUILD: perl build.pl
REFERENCES: http://bsravanin.blogspot.com/search/label/vxperf2